            "notes": "The focus of this deck is to build a fast-paced aggressive strategy around the commander Spider-Man 2099. It includes a mix of counter spells, burn spells, and efficient creatures to apply pressure on the opponent quickly. The deck aims to control the board early on with cheap interaction like Lightning Bolt and Force Spike, while using cards like True-Name Nemesis and Malcom, Alluring Scoundrel to close out the game swiftly. The mana base is optimized to support the aggressive game plan with lands like Scalding Tarn and Volcanic Island. By utilizing a mix of disruption, card advantage, and consistent threats, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent before they can stabilize."
